        "Identify the hazards, including asbestos fibres, respiratory disease, contaminated waste, and decide who could be affected.",
        "Confirm the official source, owner/client requirement, manufacturer instruction, and site rule that apply. {{cite:ohsr-part-6}}",
        "Prepare or update the required document set, including asbestos inventory or survey.",
