        "Review this article with [[lockout|Lockout]] and any site-specific procedure that applies.",
        "Identify the hazards, including electrical shock, stored energy, pressure release, unexpected motion, and decide who could be affected.",
        "Confirm the official source, owner/client requirement, manufacturer instruction, and site rule that apply. {{cite:ohsr-part-10}}",
