    "summary": "Fall Rescue Plan is a BC construction safety topic for the planned work. It helps supervisors, CSOs, employers, prime contractors, and workers understand the hazards, documents, controls, and stop-work triggers before the work starts. It connects directly to [[fall-protection|Fall Protection]] and [[fall-arrest|Fall Arrest]] so readers can move through the topic the way they would in a practical wiki.",
