        "Hearing conservation program where required: records who checked the condition before work started. {{cite:ohsr-part-8}}",
        "Hearing protection selection record: supports follow-up if a deficiency, refusal, incident, or source-review question arises. {{cite:worksafebc-ohs-regulation}}",
