        "Define the exact task, location, workers, equipment, materials, and expected duration.",
        "Review this article with [[hearing-protection|Hearing Protection]] and any site-specific procedure that applies.",
        "Identify the hazards, including noise-induced hearing loss, impulse noise, communication interference, and decide who could be affected.",
        "Confirm the official source, owner/client requirement, manufacturer instruction, and site rule that apply. {{cite:ohsr-part-7}}",
        "Prepare or update the required document set, including noise exposure assessment.",
